reviews.reviewTitle: Functional, but Size May Be an Issue for Some
reviews.reviewText: The foldable car trash can is a practical solution for keeping your vehicle tidy. It's made from water-resistant PU Leather, which contributes to its longevity. The interior lining is PEVA, a material that doesn't absorb moisture, making it easy to clean with just wipes.The trash can boasts a large storage space of up to 3 gallons, which can be a double-edged sword. While it's great for storing kids' toys or tablets, it can be a bit too bulky for smaller vehicles like sedans or small SUVs. The adjustable strap is 18" long, making it versatile for different car interiors.The reinforced front and back walls made from PP plastic board keep the can from collapsing, ensuring it retains its shape whether it's hanging on the headrest or placed on the floor. However, it's worth noting that the can may encroach on the passenger seating space when full.One of its unique features is the two clips on both sides for fastening a trash bag. This not only helps keep the can clean but also makes garbage disposal a breeze. The foldable design is a nice touch, making it portable for travel and camping.In conclusion, if you don't mind the size, this car trash can is a sturdy and convenient addition to your vehicle.
Perfect car trash solution. This little trash can is perfect, hangs off the passenger seat or sits on the floor. Has a waterproof liner. Great size. No issues.

reviews.reviewTitle: Keep your vehicle or trailer neat and tidy
reviews.reviewText: This 3-gallon travel garbage bin is a great solution for family haulers work trucks, and even travel trailers. It is very easy to use and is compatible with most small kitchen garbage bags. The clips on every side of the bun are nice as they hold the side of the bag in place preventing any issue with it folding in. The strap to place it is very nice and easy to use, I also really like that it is adjustable making it versatile to the space you need it in. We are currently using this in our family hauler and it has made a world of difference. If my teens have snacks or we stop on the go for a bite to eat it makes cleaning up after a breeze. I also really like its size it is bigger but doesn't take up too much room and can be folded and stored away when not in use. This is leakproof, we did a test by pouring some water in the base to see what would happen. Not a drop spilled, and due to it being PU leather, it was very easy to wipe clean and back, making it a great addition that is easy to maintain. Help keep the garbage and clutter under control on the go.
